cloc counts blank lines, comment lines, and physical lines of source code in many programming languages.
Hosting git repositories -- Gitolite allows you to setup git hosting on a central server, with very fine-grained access control and many (many!) more powerful features.
MySQLTuner is a script written in Perl that will assist you with your MySQL configuration and make recommendations for increased performance and stability.
A simple static site generator for photoessays
SICP PDF with Texinfo and LaTeX source
A minimal dark Theme for Sublime Text 2 and 3
OWASP ModSecurity Core Rule Set (CRS) Project (Official Repository)
A multi-language port of Browserscope's user agent parser.
Simple script to analyse your PostgreSQL database configuration, and give tuning advice
a tool for backing up your data using rsync (if you want to get help, use https://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/rsnapshot-discuss)
**ack 2 is no longer being maintained. ack 3 is the latest version.**

Imapsync is an IMAP transfers tool. The purpose of imapsync is to migrate IMAP accounts or to backup IMAP accounts. IMAP is one of the three current standard protocols to access mailboxes, the two others are POP3 and HTTP with webmails, webmails are often tied to an IMAP server. Upstream website is
Main repository for munin master / node / plugins
Linux Exploit Suggester; based on operating system release number
Real-time analysis and diagnostics tools for OpenResty (including NGINX, LuaJIT, ngx_lua, and more) based on SystemTap
Powerful and flexible web-based server management control panel
A utility for downloading TV and radio programmes from BBC iPlayer
